results.description:
Spotify is now free on mobile and tablet. Listen to the right music, wherever you are. 

With Spotify, you have access to a world of music.  You can listen to artists and albums, or create your own playlist of your favorite songs.  Want to discover new music?  Choose a ready-made playlist that suits your mood or get personalized recommendations.

Listen for free on mobile
• Play any artist, album, or playlist on shuffle mode

Listen for free on tablet
• Play any song, any time

Spotify Premium features
• Play any song, any time on any device--mobile, tablet, or your computer
• Download music for offline listening.
• Enjoy amazing sound quality.
• No ads – just uninterrupted music.
• No commitment - cancel any time you like.

Love Spotify? 
Like us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/spotify 
Follow us on Twitter: http://twitter.com/spotify

Spotify gives you instant access to millions of songs on your iPhone, iPad & iPod Touch. Try Spotify for free, or subscribe to Spotify Premium.
results.releaseNotes:
First, an apology from us. We know there were some issues introduced in the last release. We've been getting through a lot of coffee trying to fix them, and things should get a lot better with this release! Thanks for bearing with us.

• New: Introducing Your Music, a better way to save, organise and browse your favourite music.
• New: Play the same song over and over with Repeat One. Now available for Premium users and free users on iPad.
• Fixed: Smoother track skipping.
• Fixed: We've banished some crashes.
• Fixed: You can now delete Radio stations.
